data.description: Home sweet home! We are pleased to exclusively offer for sale this unique property that features a 4bd/2.5ba, with additional bonus rooms. Four bedrooms are on the second level, and two additional rooms on the lower level. One room can be used as home office or bonus room, while the other is a conversion. Property comes with a fully functional two-car garage. In addition, there is a fully enclosed large patio that is being used as an additional family and multi-purpose room. In total, there are six bedrooms, a living room, a family room, and one multipurpose room. There are carpet and tile flooring throughout, bathrooms with vanity, and large kitchen area with separate dining area and abundant cabinet and storage space. Rooms have large closets and plenty of storage space. The great room is a suite, very comfortable and cozy. Property features a large backyard with ample space for family gatherings and entertainment. Close to the freeway, parks, shopping centers and other amenities.
